        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIndeed it seems that ansible does not care about order so you can get bridges before ethernet interfaces even though in linux they are actually ordered. I really don't get this, and not sure how to proceed. I mean we could make things configurable, but I would like to have a first version that at least works in most of the standard cases before thinking about that stuff.",
