        "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nDo you prefer this?\nI know that the ip variable may be wrongly named and undocumented, but treat this as POC if you want. In general, i placed ip for everything in inventory except resource server for consistency, maybe resource server should have that too for the same reason, not sure what you think.\nAnd, i left netaddr installation, we don't need it but at least we can use ipaddr filter later.",
